<p>
The App does not require users to create an account or sign in.
</p>

<p>
The App does not collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, or home address.
</p>

<p>
If advertising or analytics services are enabled, anonymous technical information such as device information, app performance, or advertising identifiers may be collected automatically by third-party services.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>The App may use the following services:</p>

<ul>
<li>Google Play Services</li>
