</ul>

<p>
These services may collect anonymous information according to their own privacy policies.
</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>
The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.
Any changes will be published on this page with an updated effective date.
